ormat data di Firestore%0A%0A### 4. Timezone Issues%0A- Function menggunakan timezone Asia/Jakarta%0A- Pastikan borrowDate format dd/MM/yyyy%0A%0A## Security Rules%0A%0APastikan Firestore rules mengizinkan:%0A%60%60%60javascript%0A// Allow functions to read/write notifications%0Amatch /notifications/%7Bdocument%7D %7B%0A allow read, write: if request.auth != null;%0A%7D%0A%0A// Allow functions to read transactions%0Amatch /transactions/%7Bdocument%7D %7B%0A allow read: if request.auth != null;%0A%7D%0A%0A// Allow functions to update user FCM tokens%0Amatch /users/%7BuserId%7D %7B%0A allow update: if request.auth != null && request.auth.uid == userId;%0A%7D%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A## Monitoring dan Analytics%0A%0A### Metrics yang Dipantau%0A- Jumlah notifikasi terkirim per hari%0A- Success rate pengiriman FCM%0A- Jumlah buku terlambat%0A- Response time function%0A%0A### Logs%0A- Function execution logs%0A- FCM delivery reports%0A- Error tracking%0A%0A## Maintenance%0A%0A### Regular Tasks%0A1. Monitor function performance%0A2. Update dependencies secara berkala%0A3. Cleanup old notifications (optional)%0A4. Review dan optimize query performance%0A%0A### Scaling Considerations%0A- Function timeout: 540 detik (default)%0A- Concurrent executions: 1000 (default)%0A- Memory: 256MB (default)%0A%0AUntuk load yang lebih besar, pertimbangkan:%0A- Batch processing%0A- Pagination untuk query besar%0A- Increase function resources
